snippet.title: The War in Chiapas | Latin American Games Showcase TGA 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
The War in Chiapas
A fictional stealth and pixel art game inspired by real events. The player has to create his own guerrilla in Chiapas, in the context of the "dirty war" of the 80s in Latin America.
